=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Deals Only</a>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"navbar-collapse collapse\">\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Our Store</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\">About Us</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://contact.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ContactUserNextGen&recipient=dealsonlywebstore\">Contact Us</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"main-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/Hobby_Tools/Geology_Kit_Toolbag_update_2022_02_v12.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<h3>Product Details</h3>\n\t\t\t<!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n\t\t\t<div class=\"product-specs\">\n\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">TTGEOKIT13</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">810058480521</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">BEGINNER ROCK HOUNDING KIT: Included in this 13pc geology kit are the right tools to set yourself up for success in the field; from breaking up deposits to cleaning and examining materials, fossil hunting has never been so easy</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ESSENTIAL ROCK PICK HAMMER: A must have in the field is this 20oz hammer with shock absorbing rubber grip; measuring 11 inches in length and forged from one solid piece of steel, one side of the hammer head features a square face for hammering rock or driving chisels, while the pointed tip allows you to crack open rocks or hard, dense material</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ROCK HOUNDING ACCESSORIES: Once you’ve made a mess in the field, you’re going to need to sort, examine and tidy up any new found materials; this kit includes a mini steel wire mesh classifier to screen off larger unwanted raw materials, examination brushes and a snifter bottle for more detailed cleaning work, and a magnification loupe for examination</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PORTABLE TOOLS: The included nylon tool bag makes it easy to carry all your geology rock hounding equipment to and from site, keeping everything organized and in one place; the tool bag features easily accessible side pockets, a zipper closure and large middle compartment for all your equipment</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">KIT COMPONENTS INCLUDE: x1 rock pick hammer, x1 pair unisex work gloves, x1 loupe, x1 pair safety goggles, x1 pick shovel, x6 cleaning brushes, x1 mini classifier sieve, x1 snifter bottle, x6 plastic storage bags, x1 carabiner, x1 aluminum organizer, x1 chisel and x1 pair tweezers</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor 13pc Beginner Geology Rock Hounding Kit with Mining Tools and Carry Bag</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">149.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>If rock hounding, gem hunting or fossil finding are your outdoor hobby or keen geological interest, you’ll need the right tools to set yourself up for success in the field. From breaking up deposits and sorting material, to cleaning and examining your newfound precious metals, rocks, minerals, fossils, gems and more, this ASR Outdoor 13pc Beginner’s Geology Rock Hounding kit has you covered from start to finish!\n\nThis beginner geology rock hounding kit includes the following components: \n\n- Compact 2 in 1 Pick Shovel\n- Unisex work gloves, universal fit\n- Magnification jeweler’s loupe \n- x1 pair of tweezers and x1 chisel\n- Large nylon tool bag and carabiner\n- Aluminum containers for material organization\n- Dual-sided, steel unibody rock pick hammer (with rubberized, shock protection grip)\n- Adjustable Plastic Safety Goggles (with side vents to prevent fogging)\n- Sorting and Clean Up Tools: 5.5-inch mini steel mesh wire sieve, x6 brushes, 4oz snifter bottle, x6 plastic baggies \n\nAn essential in the field and stand out component of this kit is this 20oz hammer with rubberized grip for shock reduction; measuring 11 inches in length and forged from one solid piece of steel, one side of the hammer head features a square face for hammering rock or driving chisels, while the pointed tip allows you to crack open rocks or hard, dense material.\n\nThis rock hounding, gem hunting or fossil mining kit comes will all the aforementioned components that conveniently fit into a large and sturdy nylon tool bag. The storage bag makes it easy to carry all your rock hounding tools to and from site, keeping everything organized and in one place; the tool bag features handy, easily accessible side pockets too!\n\nWhether you’re on the hunt for emeralds in North Carolina, for jade in Big Sur, California or fossils in Wyoming, this rock hounding kit from ASR Outdoor will have you organized and prepared for your next mineral mining adventure. Good luck!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t<table>&nbsp;</table>\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
